249
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,059
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, 100%.

250
00:21:56,619 --> 00:21:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je nekako najrelevantnija, ono, usporedba.

251
00:21:59,079 --> 00:22:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] I, ne znam, meni su ti muški spustavi.

252
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kidsville je još, mislim, težak je, zahtjevan je, ali postoji tu, recimo, Bormio.

253
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je u Italiji.

254
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] To je pogiveno.

255
00:22:13,759 --> 00:22:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

256
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam kako ti dečki to istraže.

257
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:19,339
